Kaito and Sora, you may have to cover your ears. :D This one was 
"Ruthless". I only got to know OGDavo so too speak as opposed to lilDavo 
and Davo. A very decorative background in all stages and never a bad 
word mentioned from both the vert side and street side of things. 
Boys, you won't understand now but he was the Mayor of Sydney. Then one day, 
I bumped into him and he mentioned that was leaving. Sure enough 
10 years in Japan and he returns with you two. Nice work Mr! :D
